Not really a vscache conflict issue, but I get lots of changes t the sheet.txt files which is just in the ordering of the mappings for each of the rows.
don't think that spreadsheets were actually changed for that part, anyone else get this too?
someone made changes without building, or they decided not to commit the sheet.txt. Committers: you should always commit the .sheet.txt file along with a spreadsheet when you commit
